__bs__ But in the brain , the consequences of falling behind may be much greater than the embarrassment of dirty countertops , because when it comes to cleaning the brain , it is the very health and function of the mind and the body that &apos;s at stake , which is why understanding these very basic housekeeping functions of the brain today may be critical for preventing and treating diseases of the mind tomorrow .
