__bs__ I &apos;d like to share with you a discovery that I made a few months ago while writing an article for Italian Wired .
__bs__ I always keep my thesaurus handy whenever I &apos;m writing anything , but I &apos;d already finished editing the piece , and I realized that I had never once in my life looked up the word &quot; &quot; disabled &quot; &quot; to see what I &apos;d find .
