__bs__ So , again , transformation , adaptation , is our greatest human skill .
__bs__ And , perhaps , until we &apos;re tested , we don &apos;t know what we &apos;re made of .
__bs__ Maybe that &apos;s what adversity gives us : a sense of self , a sense of our own power .
__bs__ So , we can give ourselves a gift .
